OL,6,CG1964FThe unconfirmed date of BBC Test
OL,7,FCard C's retirement. It was replaced on
OL,8,FBBC One by Test Card D. Test Card E
OL,9,F(intended for 625-line) appeared from
OL,10,F20th April 1964 on BBC Two. However,
OL,11,FTest Card E was not well liked within
OL,12,Fthe trade and was replaced by a
OL,13,Fmodified version of Test Card C (on BBC
OL,14,FTwo).
